Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[dumba]] (Pyramid) chivakwa chine zviso zvese zvokunze (tisingaverenge hwaro) zvakaumbwa kuita gonyanhatu uye zviso izvi zvichinosangana pachimiso chiri pachisuvi.  Hwaro hwe[[dumba]] hunogona kunge hwakaumbwa kuva chero ipi zvayo [[gonyazhinji]] ''(polygon)''. Izvi zvinoreva kuti [[dumba]] rine zviso zvakaumbwa kuva [[gonyanhatu]] zvinoverengwa kuva zvitatu kana kuraudza. [[Dumba retsazano]] ndiro rinowonekwa kazhinji.

==Kupiwa kwezita==

Shoko rokuti [[dumba]] rinotoredzera kubva pachiumbwa chinoonekwa kana tichitema mashanga echigabe nokuamisa kuita matumba. Kune matumba ariko nhasi kunyika ye[[Egypt]] ayo akavakwa kuti ave nzvimbo yaivigwa anaPharoah madzimambo e[[Egypt]]. [[Dumba]] ratinoona pakuwunganidza mashanga echibage harifanane kuti gedye-gedye nematumba ari ku[[Egypt]]; iri zita rapiwa nokuti ndiro riri pedyo pakucherechedza kuumbwa kwakaitwa [[dumba]]

==Mhando dzeDumba==

Tiri muchidzidzo Kupimanzimbo, kune marudzi ematumba anodanwa zvakasiyana zvichienderana nechiumbwa chiri pahwaro hwedumba racho. Sokuti kune: [[dumba regonyanhanhatu]] (hexagonal pyramid); kwoita [[dumba retsazano]] (square based pyramid); [[dumba regonyanhatu]] (triangular pyramid); [[dumba regonyaina tsazamakonya]] (rectangular pyramid), zvichingodaro.

